<h1> <%=@owner.owner_name%> </h1>

This owner has <%=@pets.count%> pets.
<br>
<br>
Here are the pets <%=@owner.owner_name%> owns: <br><br>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Name</th>
      <th>Breed</th>
      <th>Age</th>
      <th colspan="3"></th>
    </tr>
  </thead>

  <tbody>
    <% @pets.each do |pet| %>
      <tr>
        <td><%= pet.name %></td>
        <td><%= pet.breed %></td>
        <td><%= pet.age %></td>
      </tr>
    <% end %>
  </tbody>
</table>